init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien is a bit confused by the fact that the humans are not sending a rescue mission, but are instead sending a single individual.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien had not only kidnapped Matt Damon, but also the rest of the crew from The Martian.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Dennis Rodman was able to convince the alien to send all the humans back to Earth, and to give him a chance to convince them
